message: >-
  If you use this software in your research, please cite it using the
  metadata below, or refer to the published paper in IEEE Access.

title: >-
  Simulation Code for: On the Performance of Low-Altitude UAV-Enabled
  Secure AF Relaying with Cooperative Jamming and SWIPT

authors:
  - family-names: Tatar Mamaghani
    given-names: Milad
