  - family-names: Hong
    given-names: Yi

version: "1.0.0"
date-released: "2019-01-01"
license: MIT
repository-code: "https://github.com/<your-username>/UAV-PLS-SWIPT-Relay"  # update before publishing
url: "https://doi.org/10.1109/ACCESS.2019.2948384"

abstract: >-
  MATLAB simulation code accompanying the IEEE Access paper on physical layer
  security of a low-altitude UAV-enabled cooperative relay system with
  simultaneous wireless information and power transfer (SWIPT) and cooperative
  jamming. The code reproduces the closed-form analytical expressions and
  Monte Carlo simulations for connection probability, intercept probability,
  ergodic secrecy rate, and secrecy outage probability.

keywords:
  - UAV relay
  - physical layer security
  - SWIPT
  - cooperative jamming
  - Rician fading
  - secrecy rate
  - power splitting
  - decode-and-forward
  - MATLAB simulation

